{
  "stem": "893.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I picked that name out of, out of the-- not a telephone book-- but out of the advertisements that the local paper ran.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I get, I got a birth certificate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I guess that was sufficient.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One of the Jewish people who, I guess, who paid up, paid off someone who, who stole some of the forms, printed forms.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we made-- there was a fellow who was sort of an artist who copied the seal with a rubber-- it was a, it was a seal of Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They copied it on a-- they lifted it, actually, with a gelatin, a gelatin-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that was-- they, they knew-- they had a trick.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They lifted it, and then they applied it against-- they got a negative print.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they put it on the picture and, and on the seal.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that was-- so I had something to identify myself in case they stopped me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Later on, my-- after things got worse in Slovakia, they-- my parents decided to send my younger brother, who is still alive and lives close by, to Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After crossing the border-- there was a Jewish person who still lived under the Slovakia, protection of the Slovakian police, whom he paid up.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was the-- he actually paid off, paid the police to, not to, not to bother the Jewish people who come, came across the border.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And his name was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Supposedly, he was also an informer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some people claimed he was an informer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For the Slovakians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On Jews.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Certain Jews.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Certain Jews, he was doing a favor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Certain Jews--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was a Jewish person.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was, some people said he was an informer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So after he, my brother came across the border, he came with several other people.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
